\c 5
\s UDavida ubusa ilizwe lonke lakoIsrayeli
\p
\v 1 Khona zonke izizwe zakoIsrayeli zeza kuDavida eHebroni\x + 1 Lan. 11.1-9. 1 Lan. 12.23-40.\x*, zakhuluma zisithi: Khangela, thina silithambo lakho lenyama yakho\x + Gen. 29.14.\x*.
\v 2 Lesikhathini esidlulileyo, uSawuli eseyinkosi phezu kwethu, nguwe owakhupha lowangenisa uIsrayeli\x + 1 Sam. 18.13.\x*, leN\nd kosi\nd* yathi kuwe: Wena uzakwelusa abantu bami uIsrayeli, lawe uzakuba ngumbusi phezu kukaIsrayeli\x + 7.7. 1 Sam. 16.1,12. Hlab. 78.71,72.\x*.
\v 3 Ngakho kwafika bonke abadala bakoIsrayeli enkosini uDavida eHebroni\x + 2.3.\x*; inkosi uDavida yasisenza isivumelwano labo eHebroni\x + 3.12,13,21. 2 Kho. 11.17. 1 Sam. 18.3.23.18.\x* phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 1 Sam. 23.18. Hlu. 11.11.\x*\nd*; basebemgcoba uDavida, waba yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli.
\p
\v 4 UDavida wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amathathu ekubeni kwakhe yinkosi; wabusa iminyaka engamatshumi amane\x + 1 Lan. 26.31. 29.27.\x*.
\v 5 EHebroni wabusa phezu kukaJuda iminyaka eyisikhombisa lenyanga eziyisithupha; leJerusalema wabusa iminyaka engamatshumi amathathu lantathu phezu kukaIsrayeli wonke loJuda\x + 2.11. 1 Lan. 3.4. 1 Kho. 2.11. 1 Lan. 29.27.\x*.
\s UDavida uthatha inqaba yeZiyoni
\p
\v 6 Inkosi labantu bayo basebesiya eJerusalema\x + Hlu. 1.21.\x* kumaJebusi, abahlali belizwe\x + Josh. 15.63.\x*; akhuluma kuDavida athi: Kawuyikungena lapha, ngaphandle kokuthi ususe iziphofu labaqhulayo; besithi uDavida kayikungena lapho.
\v 7 Kodwa uDavida wayithumba inqaba yeZiyoni; le ngumuzi kaDavida\x + 5.9. 1 Kho. 2.10. 8.1.\x*.
\v 8 UDavida wasesithi ngalolosuku: Ngulowo lalowo otshaya umJebusi, katshaye emgelweni wamanzi abaqhulayo leziphofu, abazondwa ngumphefumulo kaDavida\x + Hlab. 42.7.\x*. Ngakho bathi: Isiphofu loqhulayo kabayikungena endlini\x + 6.6. 8.4,18. 21.19. 23.8. 1 Lan. 11.6. Gen. 30.27.\x*.
\v 9 Ngakho uDavida wahlala enqabeni, wayibiza \add ngokuthi\add* ngumuzi kaDavida. UDavida wakha inhlangothi zonke, kusukela eMilo kusiya phakathi\x + 1 Kho. 9.15,24. 11.27. 2 Kho. 12.20. 2 Lan. 32.5. Hlu. 9.6,20.\x*.
\v 10 UDavida waqhubeka njalo esiba lamandla, njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wamabandla, yayilaye.
\p
\v 11 UHiramu inkosi yeTire wasethuma izithunywa kuDavida\x + 1 Kho. 5.1.\x*\x + 1 Lan. 14.1-16.\x*, lezigodo zemisedari, lababazi bezigodo lababazi bamatshe; basebemakhela uDavida indlu.
\v 12 UDavida wasekwazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* yayimmisile ukuthi abe yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli, lokuthi iwuphakamisile umbuso wakhe ngenxa yabantu bayo uIsrayeli\x + Nani 24.7.\x*.
\s Abantwana bakaDavida abazalelwa eJerusalema
\p
\v 13 UDavida wasethatha\x + 1 Lan. 3.5-9.\x* abanye abafazi abancane labafazi bevela eJerusalema, esevela eHebroni\x + Dute. 17.17.\x*, njalo kwakulamanye amadodana lamadodakazi azalelwa uDavida.
\v 14 Njalo la ngamabizo alabo abazalelwa yena eJerusalema: OShamuwa, loShobabi, loNathani, loSolomoni,
\v 15 loIbihari, loElishuwa, loNefegi, loJafiya,
\v 16 loElishama, loEliyada, loElifeleti.
\s UDavida unqoba amaFilisti
\p
\v 17 Kwathi amaFilisti esezwile ukuthi bamgcobile uDavida ukuthi abe yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli, wonke amaFilisti enyuka ukuyamdinga uDavida; uDavida wakuzwa, wehlela enqabeni\x + 23.14. 1 Sam. 22.4,5. 1 Lan. 11.16. 1 Lan. 14.8.\x*.
\v 18 AmaFilisti esefikile asabalala\x + 5.22. Hlu. 15.9.\x* esihotsheni seRefayimi\x + 5.22. 23.13. Josh. 15.8. 18.16. 1 Lan. 11.15. Josh. 17.15.\x*.
\v 19 UDavida wasebuza eN\nd kosi\nd*ni esithi: Ngingenyukela yini kumaFilisti? Uzawanikela esandleni sami yini? IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuDavida: Yenyuka, ngoba isibili ngizawanikela amaFilisti esandleni sakho\x + Nani 27.21.\x*.
\v 20 UDavida wasefika eBhali-Perazimi\x + Isa. 28.21.\x*, uDavida wawatshaya khona, wathi: IN\nd kosi\nd* izifohlele izitha zami phambi kwami njengokufohla kwamanzi. Ngakho wabiza ibizo laleyondawo \add ngokuthi\add* yiBhali-Perazimi.
\v 21 Asetshiya izithombe zawo lapho, loDavida labantu bakhe bazisusa\x + 1 Lan. 14.12. Dute. 7.5,25.\x*.
\p
\v 22 AmaFilisti asebuya enyuka futhi, asabalala esihotsheni seRefayimi\x + 5.22. Hlu. 15.9.\x*.
\v 23 Lapho uDavida ebuza iN\nd kosi\nd*, yathi: Ungenyuki; bhoda ngemuva kwawo, uwasukele usuka maqondana lezihlahla zebhalisamu\x + 5.19.\x*.
\v 24 Kuzakuthi-ke lapho usizwa isisinde sokuhamba ezihlokweni zezihlahla zebhalisamu, lapho uphangise\x + 2 Kho. 7.6.\x*, ngoba ngalesosikhathi iN\nd kosi\nd* izaphuma phambi kwakho ukutshaya ibutho lamaFilisti\x + Hlu. 4.14.\x*.
\v 25 UDavida wasesenza njalo, njengokumlaya kwayo iN\nd kosi\nd*, wawatshaya amaFilisti kusukela eGeba uze ufike eGezeri\x + Josh. 10.33.\x*.
